  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/22d979ac7a9a49590d3ca824b092da7d.poster.avif?t=1773435517\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/22d979ac7a9a49590d3ca824b092da7d.webm?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/22d979ac7a9a49590d3ca824b092da7d.mp4?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between float, bottom, spinning, and casting methods. Use hundreds of items, customize your gear, and adapt your approach based on weather, time of day, and fish behavior. With an improved underwater camera system, functional sonar, and controller support, every moment is immersive and responsive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/c47b72a57151ec614b5b63c9d3ffe6e6.poster.avif?t=1773435517\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/c47b72a57151ec614b5b63c9d3ffe6e6.webm?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/c47b72a57151ec614b5b63c9d3ffe6e6.mp4?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel to diverse locations across the globe, from peaceful lakes to powerful coastal waters. Play solo or with others in multiplayer. Tackle tournaments, complete daily quests, or relax in sandbox mode where everything is unlocked from the start. For those who seek more challenge, the realistic mode strips away all assists for a truly demanding experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/3e35a3e1172303a2793311563c8748d2.poster.avif?t=1773435517\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/3e35a3e1172303a2793311563c8748d2.webm?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/3e35a3e1172303a2793311563c8748d2.mp4?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From tiny roach to massive tiger sharks, Ultimate Fishing Simulator 2 features a wide variety of fish across freshwater and saltwater locations. Each species is brought to life with natural animations, authentic behaviors, and realistic size and weight variation. Some are cautious and elusive, others are aggressive and put up a serious fight - every catch is a unique encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/6a7c9f7f916a7a95c744828e88b15cc5.poster.avif?t=1773435517\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/6a7c9f7f916a7a95c744828e88b15cc5.webm?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/6a7c9f7f916a7a95c744828e88b15cc5.mp4?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Float, bottom, spinning, and casting fishing styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>60+ fish</strong> species with realistic behavior and fight mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Underwater camera view</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Singleplayer and <strong>multiplayer</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trophy Room with aquariums to showcase your best catches</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Global locations, including lakes, rivers, canals, and tropical coasts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wide range of fishing gear</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller support with vibration feedback</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily quests, tournaments, and ranking events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple difficulty modes, including normal, realistic, and <strong>SANDBOX</strong></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/22d979ac7a9a49590d3ca824b092da7d.poster.avif?t=1773435517\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/22d979ac7a9a49590d3ca824b092da7d.webm?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/22d979ac7a9a49590d3ca824b092da7d.mp4?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose between float, bottom, spinning, and casting methods. Use hundreds of items, customize your gear, and adapt your approach based on weather, time of day, and fish behavior. With an improved underwater camera system, functional sonar, and controller support, every moment is immersive and responsive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/c47b72a57151ec614b5b63c9d3ffe6e6.poster.avif?t=1773435517\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/c47b72a57151ec614b5b63c9d3ffe6e6.webm?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/c47b72a57151ec614b5b63c9d3ffe6e6.mp4?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel to diverse locations across the globe, from peaceful lakes to powerful coastal waters. Play solo or with others in multiplayer. Tackle tournaments, complete daily quests, or relax in sandbox mode where everything is unlocked from the start. For those who seek more challenge, the realistic mode strips away all assists for a truly demanding experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/3e35a3e1172303a2793311563c8748d2.poster.avif?t=1773435517\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/3e35a3e1172303a2793311563c8748d2.webm?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/3e35a3e1172303a2793311563c8748d2.mp4?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From tiny roach to massive tiger sharks, Ultimate Fishing Simulator 2 features a wide variety of fish across freshwater and saltwater locations. Each species is brought to life with natural animations, authentic behaviors, and realistic size and weight variation. Some are cautious and elusive, others are aggressive and put up a serious fight - every catch is a unique encounter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/6a7c9f7f916a7a95c744828e88b15cc5.poster.avif?t=1773435517\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/6a7c9f7f916a7a95c744828e88b15cc5.webm?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1136380/extras/6a7c9f7f916a7a95c744828e88b15cc5.mp4?t=1773435517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Float, bottom, spinning, and casting fishing styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>60+ fish</strong> species with realistic behavior and fight mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Underwater camera view</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Singleplayer and <strong>multiplayer</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trophy Room with aquariums to showcase your best catches</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Global locations, including lakes, rivers, canals, and tropical coasts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wide range of fishing gear</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller support with vibration feedback</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily quests, tournaments, and ranking events</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Multiple difficulty modes, including normal, realistic, and <strong>SANDBOX</strong></p></li></ul>",
